content:
I’ve been trying to think through the dominoes of a Russia invades Ukraine scenario.. 
All I’ve got is:
1. Further escalation of gas geopolitics, higher energy prices.
2. Higher crude oil, bc WAR
3. Lower US Dollar, bc likely losing hegemony.
4. Gold higher
5. Softs higher
